# Taxonomy YAML and generated seed SQL

- **`docs/quizymode_taxonomy.yaml`** is the only hand-edited source for category + navigation keyword structure. Keep it human-friendly (nested `description` + `keywords` maps as today).
- **`docs/quizymode_taxonomy_seed.sql`** is **generated**. Do not edit it by hand.
- After any change to `quizymode_taxonomy.yaml`, regenerate and commit both files:

```bash
dotnet run --project tools/Quizymode.TaxonomySqlGen
```

- The API applies that SQL in **one transaction** at startup (see `DatabaseSeederHostedService`). Migrations stay on EF Core; taxonomy rows come from this script.
- Parser + models live in **`src/Quizymode.Taxonomy`** (`TaxonomyYamlParser`); the generator is **`tools/Quizymode.TaxonomySqlGen`**.
